description:
Surf the web without tracking with a VPN, shield your devices with Antivirus, & guard your identity with an all-in-one app.


What's new:

* We've added an Antivirus repair option that helps you to resolve issues with Surfshark Antivirus without reinstalling the entire app;
* Our native Windows app for ARM-based devices now includes Antivirus protection;
* Experience smoother surfing with a few minor bug fixes and improvements.
